00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:37,174
Totally awesome.

287
00:14:37,176 --> 00:14:40,616
[Applause]

288
00:14:40,613 --> 00:14:42,513
And that is a quick look
at some improvements

289
00:14:42,515 --> 00:14:46,185
to the experience in El Capitan.

290
00:14:46,185 --> 00:14:50,995
[Applause]

291
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:53,890
So we saw in El Capitan
a powerful form of search

292
00:14:53,893 --> 00:14:56,733
in Spotlight that lets
you compose your searches

293
00:14:56,729 --> 00:14:58,899
in your own words.

294
00:14:58,898 --> 00:15:00,238
It knows more than ever,

