00:22:27,213 --> 00:22:30,213
And pro app makers are seeing
the benefits of Metal as well,

447
00:22:30,216 --> 00:22:32,656
people like The Foundry
and Autodesk.

448
00:22:32,651 --> 00:22:35,191
I think we are going to
see pro users, gamers,

449
00:22:35,187 --> 00:22:36,987
and all of us benefiting

450
00:22:36,989 --> 00:22:39,659
from the performance
advantages of Metal.

451
00:22:39,658 --> 00:22:43,098
So that is El Capitan,
improvements

452
00:22:43,095 --> 00:22:46,265
to experience and performance.

