01:14:22,625 --> 01:14:27,965
and as that cumulative effect
appeared, then we all start

1437
01:14:27,963 --> 01:14:30,103
to realize, oh, my
goodness, this is bigger

1438
01:14:30,099 --> 01:14:32,139
than any of us imagined.

